WEBVTT

00:00:30.010 --> 00:00:32.130
Potpisao sam hrpu papira,

00:00:32.430 --> 00:00:34.070
pokupio svoje stvari

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:36.100
i otišao do svoje žene

00:00:36.100 --> 00:00:38.370
koja me čekala u obližnjem restoranu,

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:40.320
posve zatečena.

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:43.210
Nekoliko sati kasnije,

00:00:43.620 --> 00:00:45.780
oboje smo bili zaista pijani.

00:00:45.780 --> 00:00:48.090
(Smijeh)

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:53.050
Znači, 40 i nešto godina
stalnog zaposlenja

00:00:53.060 --> 00:00:55.520
u raznim tvrtkama, velikim i malim,

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:57.020
za mene je završilo.

00:00:57.020 --> 00:01:00.030
Znao sam puno ljudi, imao dobar ugled,